{"type": "article", "id": 46783, "title": "Coach 香港退市，以及，MUJI 酒店开幕日期确定 ︳浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-11-02T03:40:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 30, "name": "Paul Smith"}, {"id": 264, "name": "MUJI"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 38292, "name": "FENTY PUMA"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 1099, "name": "资生堂"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/201711021112519AkS7oVuvGtB1r6U.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.scmp.com/business/investor-relations/article/2117913/coach-delist-hong-kong-stock-market-amid-thin-trading\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>成交量过低，Coach 从香港退市</strong></a> ︳昨日，Coach 正式改名 Tapestry，并发布公告称，由于交投量较低，公司将申请撤回在港发行的预托证券，从联交所主板退市。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/lauders-diversification-drives-growth-11040564/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>雅诗兰黛集团第一财季净利润大涨抬高股价</strong></a> ︳据雅诗兰黛集团最新财报显示，第一财季该集团的净利润大涨 45% 至 2.94 亿美元，业绩增长的主要动力来自中国市场，以及最新收购的 Too Faced 和 Becca 的品牌影响。财报发布后，雅诗兰黛集团股价大涨 9.46% 至每股 122.39 美元，目前市值约 451 亿美元。 </p><p><a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Business/Companies/Shiseido-to-book-575m-extraordinary-loss-due-to-Bare-Escentuals\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>资生堂美国业务亏损，利润预期下调 </strong></a>︳资生堂在周三表示，受美国子公司 BareMinerals 关闭近百家门店的影响，公司将出现 655 亿日元的损失。另外，资生堂将 12 月的综合利润预期下调至 100 亿日元，同比下降 69%，与之前预期的 1% 的涨幅截然相反。在 2017 年 1 月至 6 月期间，资生堂的美洲业务亏损从今年的 47 亿日元扩大至 90 亿日元。 </p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/504239\" rel=\"nofollow\">MUJI Hotel </a>的开业时间正式确定了。深圳店将率先于 2018 年 1 月 18 日开幕，北京店 3 月 20 日。另外，第三家位于银座的 MUJI Hotel 将于 2019 年春季开幕。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021103296gD7N0nVJWPBCG91.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110328FO4rTZUautS53XpE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>POLO RALPH LAUREN CHILDREN 针对日本市场首次推出了日本小学生书包。该系列书包共有三个定价不同的版本，其中，使用科尔多瓦高级皮革制作的最贵，要 20 万日元。皮革制的 11 万，人造皮革 8 万，另外还有对女孩和男孩分别推出的不同颜色的式样。 </p><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/503691\" rel=\"nofollow\">POLO RALPH LAUREN </a>小学生书包将于 11 月底接受预订，预计明年 2 月正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110407Kg7rNCsSBUdA0qIi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.744792\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110407GjDph9iR5drsntZM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110407XNJuWLrlP1zFIZnC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110407Ilnzwy7OEuYC1jeF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110407WBSqhT4xp9eCjG7z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110408MlafETYVBoHUir56.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110409heS01GY2JEM5rxjD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110408kcJrZxubt5X0gBjv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021104081JG7vtW3dUBfEhFQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.735417\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/11/kith-adidas-soccer-season-2-los-angeles-rays\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 与 KITH </a>的合作来到了第三个球队系列 LA Rays。 </p><p>该系列以深沉的棕色为主调，亮眼的橙色做点缀，另外，赞助商 Samsung 的 logo 贯穿其中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110448aEMPcUCYQVu2y8gK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021104485qteUhfCa2EPpBTA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110448UMPpu8X5StTw7sn4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021104514cn1HSI2zmbWoyAg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110453J8ZfBLPVd3b6H1jW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110454RfZJtrLAHGoDXh8p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017110211045685uwBh6g9mkqCMls.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110456910AhlWsKZqD5XoP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110457dgevGLojzFaC35WT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021104584zPqwV1tHNUY7Elf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110501QHT7AOylrijVaxXk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110503pfXhcnQKzwYtJsLS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110504xyJLN5wU6DAoHqmG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110505Ww8qs14OZIK7ukJt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110506XUJKHh8zCjWt3Iil.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110509uMiQ1Smh9a5s0tlL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110510s6uHLa7310rQWOAq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110510YJlMrGP5mfo694EL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021105120l1ALWqheGKCbYV9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110514LRfNyDMaETQxke0J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110514JakdES9RDAOe8pPv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>做凉鞋的<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/11/birkenstock-ames\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Birkenstock</a> 首次推出了运动鞋。这双全白色的鞋名为 Ames，它由麂皮混合真皮打造，目前已经登陆 Birkenstock 门店发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110537EdkZCvJesSFUKX4W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021105336QqYfSwGPsO0r3iV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021105331ivxm4KTzA6JPcgQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110533up4cPAgmh0nkDJ9Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/11/01/rihanna-puma-fenty-drop-2/#slide-29\" rel=\"nofollow\">FENTY PUMA 2017 </a>秋冬系列第二波新品现已发售，来看看都有哪些新品： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110601dqjEUeBmY6VHnaMZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110603YP4t3v0ylmIK6Whs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110559XCd8rywoNYsUPMJ6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110600gCAoSyWdH0nKb9O8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110604L4pl5jIbWcKnFtsR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110602KfRm3NvtA9BrDskz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110610jz1K38SaXBW2Y9MV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017110211060529PpSM4Z5mA3QsOv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110606N3qloTPkcDwzvbj9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110606AdcpHUWZBgYGnTVh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110601tET5GqFYsUKbhkcl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110607foUyuBKl2zQG0dRA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021106045y47tx91bZoFnSvM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021106021I6joiV29pWuxc0B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110602yMHhFkCPRm9ioYuw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110604exQ8CL4JKmfEqtTF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110608Nv50JnHtqdp9rOVF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110608cCK5daPSVUboJOjp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110609a1OfF8dvGr7UwPXT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110609zqbU4pDEkMygPNhF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110613yqdnMlIeHJFBP4Aw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110610zL18qvkIhSFRy2KM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110600X3ODW8IlkypdzhCZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110612u8b7rXKkEeclMjzo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110612IZrB6YCpc3L0fSsU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110610HlSWnf9gFPBUVL4h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021106111Fi6G8DAeXsad7fV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110612lvO0uhCtrS1q2xZz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110613qG4eQar7JMEvkyIK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-11-01/allstar100/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Converse </a>出了款使用日本传统高级织品西阵织制作的 All Star 100。这双鞋的鞋面上印有日式风情十足老虎纹样，还有高筒和低筒两个版本可以选择，售价 1.1 万日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110803msawuLiTRkAvSGWy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110759S3VMnzjaepX8RqZl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110801dVorhuPERIDkjBfK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110802din8YUkZ6rKjo5zx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110802YSRzbFi0ONoI6jLt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110804Hwc8Bv7Zebd91pNR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110804ikcdobU93GAMfrl7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711021108071AiUkD7w42edsEQF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.paulsmith.co.jp/jidori/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paul Smith</a> 为它的 2017 男式西装和大衣系列在日本打了个名为“自拍”的广告，以不同场景下的自拍为主题，着重表现了服装的灵活性和舒适性。 </p><p>片中，两名男士分别身穿正装和商务休闲装，以“不自拍就会死”为口号，在街头展开了一场自拍比拼：乒乓球桌、浴室、游泳池、酒吧都成了他们的背景。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110854U4e1aP9okhSbusMA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.560606\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110854brvAcdjk765Xz2tT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110855I8JtuAyjWG2igCqe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110855IxvQVAdPpkBm3SfW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110859pxcTfQ4qe7Uwu9nC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110859j7I5blOzy3p9DniY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110903YWs2QfOb5rlF1A3B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171102110908SHbYMed10v4PLsEB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.133333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>视频请看这里（<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1BIFrnrjvpU\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paul Smith JIDORI</a>）。</p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Paul Smith</p>"}